items.title: Appeals court allows Trump administration to remove ethics watchdog Dellinger — for now
items.description: The Supreme Court is likely to determine whether President Donald Trump can fire Hampton Dellinger as head of the Office of Special Counsel.

items.title: House censures Rep. Al Green for heckling Trump during speech to Congress
items.description: Fewer than 30 members of the House of Representatives have been censured. Green said about interrupting Trump, "Truthfully, I would do it again."
